# Frontend (Vite) — copy to `.env` locally if needed; set in your host (Vercel, etc.) for production.
# Your static site (e.g. https://www.swimily.app) does NOT serve /api — point this at your Node API origin.
# Example: https://api.swimily.app
# Leave unset for local dev (Vite proxies /api to the backend).
# VITE_API_URL=
